class Solution {
    public int reachNumber(int target) {
        int steps = 0;
        int currentPosition = 0;
        while (currentPosition != target) {
            steps++;
            currentPosition += steps;
        }
        return steps;
    }
}
```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(target)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
